
This directory serves as a regression testing and performance testing
platform for libabac.  It contains many actual valid RT0
examples in C/python/perl. It also contain examples of Creddy in
action.

creddy_prover_tests : various RT examples using Creddy and abac_prover,
                      a C implemenation of an ABAC prover
python_tests: same RT examples as in creddy_prover_tests but in python scripts
              using libabac ABAC
example_scripts: small examples scripts in perl/python/C, wiki contains examples
              used on libabac's wiki page
scaling_tests: performance testing
attr_tests: testing different types of attribute xml format
creddy_tests : a comphrensive testing of creddy


To run,

   make tests

if running on BSD,

   make -i tests


